      "type": "text",
      "x": 330,
      "y": 1722,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 55,
      "text": "goroutine per container\nnsenter → /bin/sh -c <healthcheck>\nstarting → healthy → unhealthy\nMINIBOX HEALTHCHECK label in OCI config",
