      "y": 1860,
      "width": 1140,
      "height": 36,
      "text": "SAVE: lookup manifest digest in index.json → pack {meta.json, blobs/sha256/*} into tar archive\nLOAD: unpack tar → read meta.json → upsert image reference into index.json  ·  PRUNE: GC dangling blobs + stopped container dirs",
